	<preparation>Mix meatball mixture together and roll balls in flour.  Saute in butter until throughly cooked.

Sauce:  saute crushed clove of garlic in 2 Tbl butter until soft and discard.  Add remaining ingredients and reduce until thick.  Season with salt and pepper to taste.</preparation>
